---
import ArchivePitchLayout from '@layouts/ArchivePitchLayout.astro';
---

<ArchivePitchLayout
  title="The Korman Archive — Brand Identity"
  description="Brand identity reference for The Korman Archive heritage documentation project."
>

  <!-- ======= 1. Cover ======= -->
  <section class="slide slide--ka-hero" id="slide-1">
    <div class="slide__inner">
      <div class="ka-lockup-primary ka-lockup-primary--cover">
        <span class="ka-lockup-primary__the">The</span>
        <span class="ka-lockup-primary__korman">Korman</span>
        <span class="ka-lockup-primary__archive">Archive</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ka-hero-meta">Brand Identity Reference &middot; March 2026</div>
    </div>
    <div class="scroll-hint fade-in">
      <div class="scroll-hint__arrow"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 2. Visual Direction ======= -->
  <section class="slide" id="slide-2">
    <div class="slide__inner">
      <p class="ka-section-num">09</p>
      <h2 class="slide__heading">Visual Direction</h2>
      <p class="ka-section-intro">44 documentary photographs across 7 areas of the Korman compound. Two lenses, one light, one day. Each shot specifies a type, a technique, and a lens. When the photographs are made, they drop into these layout slots with no structural changes needed.</p>
      <div class="ka-two-col">
        <div class="ka-card">
          <div class="ka-card__title">Kit</div>
          <table class="ka-spec">
            <tr><td>Camera</td><td>Leica SL3-S &middot; 24MP</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Wide</td><td>Summicron-SL 28mm f/2 &mdash; establishing, contextual, POV</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Standard</td><td>Summicron-SL 50mm f/2 &mdash; portraits, details, 50&amp;Stitch</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Light</td><td>Nanlite Pavotube 4ft &middot; bi-color &middot; battery</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Grip</td><td>Bounce board, light stand, A-clamps, gaffer tape</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Swaps</td><td>One per area &mdash; 7 total across the day</td></tr>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-card">
          <div class="ka-card__title">Areas</div>
          <table class="ka-spec">
            <tr><td>A</td><td>Cars in Build &mdash; 7 shots</td></tr>
            <tr><td>B</td><td>Concours Car &mdash; 7 shots &middot; High</td></tr>
            <tr><td>C</td><td>Ray&rsquo;s 325 &mdash; 7 shots &middot; High</td></tr>
            <tr><td>D</td><td>Dyno Area &mdash; 6 shots &middot; Contingent</td></tr>
            <tr><td>E</td><td>Engine Build &mdash; 7 shots &middot; High</td></tr>
            <tr><td>F</td><td>Ray Portraits &mdash; 5 shots &middot; Critical</td></tr>
            <tr><td>G</td><td>Warehouse &mdash; 5 shots</td></tr>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 3. 01 Positioning — Is / Is Not ======= -->
  <section class="slide" id="slide-3">
    <div class="slide__inner">
      <p class="ka-section-num">01</p>
      <h2 class="slide__heading">Positioning</h2>
      <div class="ka-two-col">
        <div class="ka-position-card ka-position-card--is">
          <div class="ka-position-card__label">The Archive Is</div>
          <ul class="ka-position-card__list">
            <li>A heritage documentation project capturing institutional knowledge</li>
            <li>The technical philosophy, competition history, and craft of Korman Autoworks</li>
            <li>A bounded sub-identity within the larger Korman brand system</li>
            <li>Warm, documentary, and precise in tone</li>
            <li>Built for researchers, enthusiasts, and the Korman family itself</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-position-card ka-position-card--isnot">
          <div class="ka-position-card__label">The Archive Is Not</div>
          <ul class="ka-position-card__list">
            <li>A marketing channel or sales funnel</li>
            <li>A replacement for the V2 product brand (Amber Theorem)</li>
            <li>A nostalgia exercise or museum piece</li>
            <li>Consumer-facing content designed for broad reach</li>
            <li>A separate company or independent entity</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 4. 01 Positioning — Origin Story ======= -->
  <section class="slide" id="slide-4">
    <div class="slide__inner">
      <p class="ka-section-num">01</p>
      <h2 class="slide__heading">Origin</h2>
      <p class="ka-section-intro">The Korman Archive exists because some things are too important to live only in the memories of the people who built them. Ray Korman&rsquo;s technical philosophy&mdash;the specific way he approached engine tolerances, the reasoning behind suspension geometry choices, the competition strategies that produced two wins at the 24 Hours of Watkins Glen&mdash;these are institutional knowledge that disappears when it isn&rsquo;t deliberately captured.</p>
      <p class="ka-section-intro">The Archive is a bounded sub-identity: warm where the V2 product brand is sharp, documentary where V2 is assertive. It shares Korman&rsquo;s DNA but speaks in a quieter register. Where Amber Theorem says &ldquo;The Ultimate Driving Machine. Finished,&rdquo; the Archive says &ldquo;Here&rsquo;s exactly how they finished it, and why.&rdquo;</p>
      <p class="ka-section-intro">The design system reflects this difference at every level&mdash;typography, color, marks, voice. What follows is the complete brand reference.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 5. C1: 325 in Front of Shop — Full-Bleed ======= -->
  <section class="slide essay-slide essay-full-bleed essay-full-bleed--scrim" id="slide-5">
    <div class="essay-full-bleed__img">
      <div class="ka-placeholder">
        <span class="ka-placeholder__id">C1</span>
        <span class="ka-placeholder__title">325 in Front of Shop</span>
        <span class="ka-placeholder__layout">Full-Bleed</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="essay-full-bleed__overlay essay-full-bleed__overlay--bottom-left">
      <p class="ka-section-num">C HERITAGE</p>
      <h3>325 in Front of Shop</h3>
      <div class="ka-shot-meta">
        <span class="ka-tag ka-tag--type">Wide w/ Subject</span>
        <span class="ka-tag ka-tag--tech">Natural Light</span>
        <span class="ka-tag ka-tag--lens">28mm</span>
      </div>
      <p>Ray&rsquo;s 325 parked in front of Korman Autoworks. Building signage visible, the car grounded in its context&mdash;Greensboro suburban-industrial, honest and undecorated. The shop facade IS the brand. Overcast or golden hour. Don&rsquo;t sanitize the setting. The industrial corridor, the parking lot, the mature trees&mdash;this is where the work happens.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 6. C4: Ray with the Car — Image-Text ======= -->
  <section class="slide essay-slide essay-image-text" id="slide-6">
    <div class="essay-image-text__image">
      <div class="ka-placeholder">
        <span class="ka-placeholder__id">C4</span>
        <span class="ka-placeholder__title">Ray with the Car</span>
        <span class="ka-placeholder__layout">Image-Text</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="essay-image-text__prose">
      <p class="ka-section-num">C HERITAGE</p>
      <h3>Ray with the Car</h3>
      <div class="ka-shot-meta">
        <span class="ka-tag ka-tag--type">Lifestyle Portrait</span>
        <span class="ka-tag ka-tag--tech">DOF f/2</span>
        <span class="ka-tag ka-tag--lens">50mm</span>
      </div>
      <p>Ray with the 325&mdash;walking around it, pointing at something, in conversation. Candid but directed. The 50 at f/2 gives portrait separation without the compression of a long lens. More honest, more documentary.</p>
      <p>This is the personal car. The narrative is the relationship between man and machine over decades. The car and Ray share the frame equally&mdash;neither dominates.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 7. C5 + C6: Undercarriage + Under-Car POV — Diptych Landscape ======= -->
  <section class="slide essay-slide essay-diptych essay-diptych--landscape" id="slide-7">
    <div class="essay-diptych__images essay-diptych__images--gap-tight">
      <div class="essay-diptych__item" style="flex:1">
        <div class="ka-placeholder">
          <span class="ka-placeholder__id">C5</span>
          <span class="ka-placeholder__title">Undercarriage</span>
          <span class="ka-placeholder__layout">Diptych</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="essay-diptych__item" style="flex:1">
        <div class="ka-placeholder">
          <span class="ka-placeholder__id">C6</span>
          <span class="ka-placeholder__title">Under-Car POV</span>
          <span class="ka-placeholder__layout">Diptych</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="essay-diptych__caption">C5: Suspension, exhaust, subframe&mdash;catalog material. Pavotube angled up from below the lifted car. &ensp;|&ensp; C6: Under the lifted car looking up. Wide, distortion intentional. The mechanic&rsquo;s perspective on the 28mm.</div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 8. 02 Marks — Primary Lockup ======= -->
  <section class="slide" id="slide-8">
    <div class="slide__inner">
      <p class="ka-section-num">02</p>
      <h2 class="slide__heading">Primary Lockup</h2>
      <p class="ka-label">Stacked mark &mdash; 4 background variants</p>
      <div class="ka-mark-grid ka-mark-grid--4">
        <div class="ka-mark-cell ka-mark-cell--dark">
          <span class="ka-mark-cell__label">Dark</span>
          <div class="ka-lockup-primary">
            <span class="ka-lockup-primary__the">The</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-primary__korman">Korman</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-primary__archive">Archive</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-mark-cell ka-mark-cell--light">
          <span class="ka-mark-cell__label">Light</span>
          <div class="ka-lockup-primary">
            <span class="ka-lockup-primary__the">The</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-primary__korman">Korman</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-primary__archive">Archive</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-mark-cell ka-mark-cell--warm">
          <span class="ka-mark-cell__label">Warm</span>
          <div class="ka-lockup-primary">
            <span class="ka-lockup-primary__the">The</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-primary__korman">Korman</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-primary__archive">Archive</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-mark-cell ka-mark-cell--mid">
          <span class="ka-mark-cell__label">Mid</span>
          <div class="ka-lockup-primary">
            <span class="ka-lockup-primary__the">The</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-primary__korman">Korman</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-primary__archive">Archive</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 9. 02 Marks — Inline Lockup ======= -->
  <section class="slide" id="slide-9">
    <div class="slide__inner">
      <p class="ka-section-num">02</p>
      <h2 class="slide__heading">Inline Lockup</h2>
      <p class="ka-label">Horizontal mark &mdash; 4 background variants</p>
      <div class="ka-mark-grid ka-mark-grid--4">
        <div class="ka-mark-cell ka-mark-cell--dark">
          <span class="ka-mark-cell__label">Dark</span>
          <div class="ka-lockup-inline">
            <span class="ka-lockup-inline__korman">Korman</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-inline__sep">|</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-inline__archive">Archive</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-mark-cell ka-mark-cell--light">
          <span class="ka-mark-cell__label">Light</span>
          <div class="ka-lockup-inline">
            <span class="ka-lockup-inline__korman">Korman</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-inline__sep">|</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-inline__archive">Archive</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-mark-cell ka-mark-cell--warm">
          <span class="ka-mark-cell__label">Warm</span>
          <div class="ka-lockup-inline">
            <span class="ka-lockup-inline__korman">Korman</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-inline__sep">|</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-inline__archive">Archive</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-mark-cell ka-mark-cell--mid">
          <span class="ka-mark-cell__label">Mid</span>
          <div class="ka-lockup-inline">
            <span class="ka-lockup-inline__korman">Korman</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-inline__sep">|</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-inline__archive">Archive</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="ka-label" style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">Small-scale use</p>
      <div class="ka-mark-grid ka-mark-grid--2">
        <div class="ka-mark-cell ka-mark-cell--dark" style="min-height: 120px; padding: 20px;">
          <div class="ka-lockup-inline ka-lockup-inline--sm">
            <span class="ka-lockup-inline__korman">Korman</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-inline__sep">|</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-inline__archive">Archive</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-mark-cell ka-mark-cell--warm" style="min-height: 120px; padding: 20px;">
          <div class="ka-lockup-inline ka-lockup-inline--sm">
            <span class="ka-lockup-inline__korman">Korman</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-inline__sep">|</span>
            <span class="ka-lockup-inline__archive">Archive</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 10. 02 Marks — Document Stamp ======= -->
  <section class="slide" id="slide-10">
    <div class="slide__inner">
      <p class="ka-section-num">02</p>
      <h2 class="slide__heading">Document Stamp</h2>
      <p class="ka-label">Standard and extended formats</p>
      <div class="ka-mark-grid ka-mark-grid--4">
        <div class="ka-mark-cell ka-mark-cell--dark">
          <span class="ka-mark-cell__label">Standard</span>
          <div class="ka-stamp">
            <span class="ka-stamp__line1">Korman Archive</span>
            <span class="ka-stamp__line2">Heritage Document</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-mark-cell ka-mark-cell--dark">
          <span class="ka-mark-cell__label">Extended</span>
          <div class="ka-stamp ka-stamp--extended">
            <span class="ka-stamp__line1">Korman Archive</span>
            <span class="ka-stamp__line2">Heritage Document</span>
            <span class="ka-stamp__catalog">KA-2026-0047</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-mark-cell ka-mark-cell--light">
          <span class="ka-mark-cell__label">Light bg</span>
          <div class="ka-stamp">
            <span class="ka-stamp__line1">Korman Archive</span>
            <span class="ka-stamp__line2">Heritage Document</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-mark-cell ka-mark-cell--warm">
          <span class="ka-mark-cell__label">Warm bg</span>
          <div class="ka-stamp">
            <span class="ka-stamp__line1">Korman Archive</span>
            <span class="ka-stamp__line2">Heritage Document</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 11. B1: Concours Car Hero — Full-Bleed ======= -->
  <section class="slide essay-slide essay-full-bleed essay-full-bleed--scrim" id="slide-11">
    <div class="essay-full-bleed__img">
      <div class="ka-placeholder">
        <span class="ka-placeholder__id">B1</span>
        <span class="ka-placeholder__title">Concours Car Hero</span>
        <span class="ka-placeholder__layout">Full-Bleed</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="essay-full-bleed__overlay essay-full-bleed__overlay--bottom-left">
      <p class="ka-section-num">B CONCOURS</p>
      <h3>Concours Car Hero</h3>
      <div class="ka-shot-meta">
        <span class="ka-tag ka-tag--type">Wide w/ Subject</span>
        <span class="ka-tag ka-tag--tech">HDR Bracket</span>
        <span class="ka-tag ka-tag--lens">28mm</span>
      </div>
      <p>Full three-quarter hero. Bay door backlight if inside, HDR bracket for the high-contrast transition between shop interior and daylight. One clean hero shot&mdash;the cover image. The glass-peened engine bay, the gold-zinc hardware, the fit-and-finish that defines Korman&rsquo;s standard. This is the car that proves the philosophy.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 12. B3: Engine Bay 50&Stitch — Image-Text ======= -->
  <section class="slide essay-slide essay-image-text" id="slide-12">
    <div class="essay-image-text__image">
      <div class="ka-placeholder">
        <span class="ka-placeholder__id">B3</span>
        <span class="ka-placeholder__title">Engine Bay &mdash; 50&amp;Stitch</span>
        <span class="ka-placeholder__layout">Image-Text</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="essay-image-text__prose">
      <p class="ka-section-num">B CONCOURS</p>
      <h3>Engine Bay</h3>
      <div class="ka-shot-meta">
        <span class="ka-tag ka-tag--type">Details</span>
        <span class="ka-tag ka-tag--tech">50&amp;Stitch</span>
        <span class="ka-tag ka-tag--lens">50mm (stitched)</span>
      </div>
      <p>The engine bay, complete. Glass-peened aluminum, gold-zinc hardware. 50&amp;Stitch for medium-format depth and resolution across the full bay&mdash;stitched panels at 24MP per frame produce a large, detailed composite.</p>
      <p>This is the defining Korman image. The technique earns its place here: enough resolution to see every fastener finish, enough depth to read the engineering philosophy at a glance. Take your time.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 13. B4 + B6: Interior Details + Paint Texture — Diptych Portrait ======= -->
  <section class="slide essay-slide essay-diptych essay-diptych--portrait" id="slide-13">
    <div class="essay-diptych__images essay-diptych__images--gap-tight">
      <div class="essay-diptych__item" style="flex:1">
        <div class="ka-placeholder">
          <span class="ka-placeholder__id">B4</span>
          <span class="ka-placeholder__title">Interior Details</span>
          <span class="ka-placeholder__layout">Diptych</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="essay-diptych__item" style="flex:1">
        <div class="ka-placeholder">
          <span class="ka-placeholder__id">B6</span>
          <span class="ka-placeholder__title">Paint &amp; Chrome</span>
          <span class="ka-placeholder__layout">Diptych</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="essay-diptych__caption">B4: Interior stitching, gauges, shift knob, pedals&mdash;each individually isolated at f/2. Consistent lighting, move close for each element. &ensp;|&ensp; B6: Paint reflection, chrome, glass-peened texture at minimum focus. The surface quality that defines the Korman standard.</div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 14. 03 Color — Flexoki Base ======= -->
  <section class="slide" id="slide-14">
    <div class="slide__inner">
      <p class="ka-section-num">03</p>
      <h2 class="slide__heading">Color &mdash; Flexoki Base</h2>
      <p class="ka-label">Neutral foundation &mdash; 11 swatches</p>
      <div class="ka-swatch-row">
        <div class="ka-swatch ka-swatch--lt" style="background: #100F0F;">
          <span class="ka-swatch__name">Black</span>
          <span class="ka-swatch__hex">#100F0F</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-swatch ka-swatch--lt" style="background: #1C1B1A;">
          <span class="ka-swatch__name">900</span>
          <span class="ka-swatch__hex">#1C1B1A</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-swatch ka-swatch--lt" style="background: #282726;">
          <span class="ka-swatch__name">850</span>
          <span class="ka-swatch__hex">#282726</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-swatch ka-swatch--lt" style="background: #343331;">
          <span class="ka-swatch__name">800</span>
          <span class="ka-swatch__hex">#343331</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-swatch ka-swatch--lt" style="background: #403E3C;">
          <span class="ka-swatch__name">700</span>
          <span class="ka-swatch__hex">#403E3C</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-swatch ka-swatch--lt" style="background: #575653;">
          <span class="ka-swatch__name">600</span>
          <span class="ka-swatch__hex">#575653</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-swatch ka-swatch--dk" style="background: #6F6E69;">
          <span class="ka-swatch__name">500</span>
          <span class="ka-swatch__hex">#6F6E69</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-swatch ka-swatch--dk" style="background: #B7B5AC;">
          <span class="ka-swatch__name">300</span>
          <span class="ka-swatch__hex">#B7B5AC</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-swatch ka-swatch--dk" style="background: #CECDC3;">
          <span class="ka-swatch__name">200</span>
          <span class="ka-swatch__hex">#CECDC3</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-swatch ka-swatch--dk" style="background: #E6E4D9;">
          <span class="ka-swatch__name">100</span>
          <span class="ka-swatch__hex">#E6E4D9</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-swatch ka-swatch--dk" style="background: #FFFCF0;">
          <span class="ka-swatch__name">Paper</span>
          <span class="ka-swatch__hex">#FFFCF0</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 15. 03 Color — Warm Scale + Exclusions ======= -->
  <section class="slide" id="slide-15">
    <div class="slide__inner">
      <p class="ka-section-num">03</p>
      <h2 class="slide__heading">Color &mdash; Warm Scale</h2>
      <p class="ka-label">Archive warm palette &mdash; Heist-derived</p>
      <div class="ka-swatch-row">
        <div class="ka-swatch ka-swatch--lt" style="background: #4A2E1B;">
          <span class="ka-swatch__name">Walnut</span>
          <span class="ka-swatch__hex">#4A2E1B</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-swatch ka-swatch--lt" style="background: #6B4226;">
          <span class="ka-swatch__name">Leather</span>
          <span class="ka-swatch__hex">#6B4226</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-swatch ka-swatch--lt" style="background: #8B5E3C;">
          <span class="ka-swatch__name">Tobacco</span>
          <span class="ka-swatch__hex">#8B5E3C</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-swatch ka-swatch--lt" style="background: #A67B5B;">
          <span class="ka-swatch__name">Saddle</span>
          <span class="ka-swatch__hex">#A67B5B</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-swatch ka-swatch--lt" style="background: #C4956A;">
          <span class="ka-swatch__name">Honey</span>
          <span class="ka-swatch__hex">#C4956A</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-swatch ka-swatch--dk" style="background: #D4A373;">
          <span class="ka-swatch__name">Clay</span>
          <span class="ka-swatch__hex">#D4A373</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="ka-label" style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">Exclusion zone &mdash; reserved for V2</p>
      <div class="ka-swatch-row">
        <div class="ka-swatch ka-swatch--lt ka-exclusion" style="background: #0066B1;">
          <span class="ka-swatch__name">Blue</span>
          <span class="ka-swatch__hex">#0066B1</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ka-swatch ka-swatch--lt ka-exclusion" style="background: #2B115A;">
          <span class="ka-swatch__name">Violet</span>
          <span class="ka-swatch__hex">#2B115A</span>
